In order to remove a task from a route plan, utilize the PUT method with the container endpoint to assign that task to a new container.URL: https://onfleet.com/api/v2/routePlans/:routePlanId/tasks
Example Request JSON{
	"tasks":[
		"Qur4QbKBP1MgpRGCAMIQ~rho",
		"p3UHDHUk7BMAanM6HsK*Dg*x",
		"178IyAxfAh8bzzpgWZbMMJYJ",
		"T615F6M~HlOx9qNJQnD2*JJo"
		]
}

ðŸš§Current UsageThis endpoint enables task(s) addition.However, this endpoint will require you to keep a list of the tasks you already have in the route plan in addtion to the task(s) you are to add.For Example, if the original task array contains Task A, B and C, and you want to add D to the route plan; the tasks array you are to provide will have to be: [A, B, C, D] instead of just [D].Otherwise, you run the risks of removing A, B, and C from the route plan.Updated 2 months ago Update Route PlanGET Route planUpdated 2 months ago Update Route PlanGET Route planQUICKSTARTQuickstart GuideGUIDESIntroductionAuthenticationTesting your API keyThrottlingData Types and Response FormatsErrorsAn invalid requestEntitiesMetadataQuerying metadataWorking with metadataThe metadata objectLimitationsSupported EntitiesStatusDeep LinkingTestingAPI WrappersScoped API KeyNo-code Integration PlatformsProof of Delivery RetrievalAPI REFERENCEOrganizationsGet delegatee detailsGet detailsAdministratorsDelete administratorUpdate administratorList administratorsCreate administratorWorkersWorker's Route Delivery ManifestSet worker's scheduleGet worker's scheduleDelete workerUpdate workerGet single workerGet workers by locationList Worker's Assigned TasksList workersCreate workerHubsList hubsUpdate HubCreate HubTeamsList Unassigned Tasks in a TeamDriver Time EstimateTeam Auto-DispatchDelete teamGet single teamList teamsUpdate teamCreate teamDestinationsDestination Address WarningsGet single destinationCreate destinationRecipientsGet single recipientFind recipientUpdate recipientCreate recipientTasksAutomatically assign list of tasksDelete taskClone taskComplete taskUpdate taskGet single task by shortIdGet single taskList tasksRecipient OverridesDependenciesCompletion RequirementsManual AssignmentAutomatic AssignmentStateBatch Job StatusTask Custom FieldsCreate tasks in batch - asyncCreate tasks in batchCreate taskContainersAdditional optionsUpdate tasksInsert tasks at index (or append)Get cont